th Jamal Ben Saddik (38-10, 29 KO) to see who moves on in the tournament. Among the other names taking part in Phase Two are Nabil Khachab (29-6-1, 4 KO), Iancu Ionut (31-11, 13 KO), Rade Opacic (21-7, 16 KO), Milos Cvjeticanin (13-4, 9 KO), Sofian Laidouni (39-5-1, 20 KO), and many more. In addition, Chico Kwasi (44-5-2, 23 KO) will defend his GLORY welterweight world title against Mehdi Ait El Hadj (35-4-2, 8 KO), Mory Kromah (34-3-1, 20 KO) returns and takes on Cristian Ristea (44-26, 13 KO) in a heavyweight match-up outside the tournament, and Tayfun Ozcan (88-11-3, 28 KO) clashes with rival Don Sno (6-2, 3 KO)." type="episode" contentRating="PG-13" duration="21279000" grandparentArt="https://dki01q1l7yn3y.cloudfront.net/thumbnails-platform-prod/assets/cs::content::shows/11056-13104/22644294-default_v1.jpeg" grandparentGuid="plex://show/6489b1f1782e547231bd91c4" grandparentKey="/library/metadata/6489b1f1782e547231bd91c4" grandparentRatingKey="6489b1f1782e547231bd91c4" grandparentThumb="https://provider-static.plex.tv/epg/cms/production/e82ff7c4-015e-440d-a8df-d960efc5d3f8/GLORY_2000x3000_Nicholas_Olsen.jpg" grandparentTitle="GLORY Kickboxing" grandparentType="show" index="8" originallyAvailableAt="2025-09-02T17:46:47Z" parentIndex="0" requiresConsent="1" skipParent="1" thumb="https://partner-upload-assets.wurl.com/glory_kickboxing/FAST_Graphics_G103.jpg" title="GLORY 103 Rotterdam LHS" userState="0" year="2025"><Image alt="GLORY 103 Rotterdam LHS" type="coverArt" url="https://dki01q1l7yn3y.cloudfront.net/thumbnails-platform-prod/assets/cs::content::shows/11056-13104/22644294-default_v1.jpeg"/><Image alt="GLORY 103 Rotterdam LHS" type="coverPoster" url="https://provider-static.plex.tv/epg/cms/production/e82ff7c4-015e-440d-a8df-d960efc5d3f8/GLORY_2000x3000_Nicholas_Olsen.jpg"/><Image alt="GLORY 103 Rotterdam LHS" type="snapshot" url="https://partner-upload-assets.wurl.com/glory_kickboxing/FAST_Graphics_G103.jpg"/><Genre filter="genre=620143f98578b9238e1cdb8a" id="